title: DP Education - O/L සිංහල මාධ්‍යය
description:
About Us
Dhammika & Priscilla Foundation is a not-for-profit organization focused on providing free quality education & healthcare facilities for all. DP Education is the digital learning platform that delivers the Foundation's vision of equal access to world-class free digital learning and healthcare in accelerating human capability development. DP Education O/L channel covers subjects such as Math, Science, Business Studies & all other O/L subjects with live classes & paper discussions.

Vision
We provide equal access to world-class digital learning, and healthcare facilities to develop  human capability to eliminate poverty.

Mission
Dedicated to transform learning and teaching experiences through free online education, best-in-class teachers, and the development of education infrastructure.

Leadership 
Dhammika Perera & Priscilla Perera are the Co-Founders of the Foundation. The overall direction of all initiatives are set by the Chairman of the Foundation, Dhammika Perera.
